{"title":"兄弟情谊——赠一位德国汉学家赵瑞蕻","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟情谊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——赠一位德国汉学家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵瑞蕻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请听一曲竹枝词，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且将古调写新诗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此地山中无翠竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但从画里看风姿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉墙上有墨竹横，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满壁图书是汉文；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹下畅饮莱因酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯前谈笑各抒情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我愿溪边翠竹栽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茂林深处有亭台；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洞箫声自青峰下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅花落尽桃花开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光烂漫竹林里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仕女齐着锦缎衣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复活节日踏青处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裙裾飘舞胜虹霓。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我愿黄河两岸间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍植白桦撑苍天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"座座高楼道旁起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁工厂冒浓烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广阔公路穿城乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车来往通四方；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邀请德国歌舞团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小城剧院好登场。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"语罢举杯同祝贺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葡萄美酒竹枝歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化交流自古有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟情谊今日多！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}